itedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:04:09.000Z","msg":"要有文宣講<br />\n77旺角警察政變<br />\n警察推翻香港法律條例"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:36:15.000Z","msg":"香港七七事變<br />\n香港警察發動政變推翻香港法律條例"},{"pid":"01b2b29d67018b2bf93d6aba2c250aadec0a700f","tid":1294084,"uid":49066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:38:13.000Z","msg":"網民定性7月7日警方行動為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察暴動</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈譴責暴徒，知法犯法</span></span>"}]}